WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:16.550
Is today <i>Reincarnated in Another 
World as a Skill Demon Lord,</i>

3
00:00:16.550 --> 00:00:20.370
<i>I Lead a Cheat Slow Life 
While Raising a Villainess</i> day?

4
00:00:20.680 --> 00:00:25.750
It's <i>Reincarnated in Another 
World as a Skill Demon Lord,</i>

5
00:00:25.750 --> 00:00:31.000
<i>I Lead a Cheat Slow Life While Raising 
a Villainess: Oops, I Did It Again</i> day.

6
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.310
So close!

7
00:00:32.690 --> 00:00:35.480
Should I wake you up 
at the usual time tomorrow morning?

8
00:00:35.480 --> 00:00:36.540
Yes, please.

9
00:00:36.880 --> 00:00:39.960
Sounds good. Good night, then.

10
00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:41.260
Good night.

11
00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.990
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

12
00:02:22.730 --> 00:02:25.530
It's time for torture, Princess!

13
00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:27.220
I surrender!

14
00:02:27.220 --> 00:02:28.270
Your Highness!

15
00:02:28.270 --> 00:02:30.830
Stop trying to set a
new record for the fastest time!

16
00:02:30.830 --> 00:02:33.350
Today's torture is...

17
00:02:33.750 --> 00:02:36.170
Ta-da! Balloon art!

18
00:02:36.540 --> 00:02:40.090
Mama made some for me the other day, 
and it was lots of fun.

19
00:02:40.090 --> 00:02:42.100
So I thought you'd like it, too.

20
00:02:43.860 --> 00:02:46.510
Listen well, daughter of the Hell-Lord.

21
00:02:47.490 --> 00:02:52.200
Balloon artists visited
the empire as street performers.

22
00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:55.100
Her Highness has seen 
the finest of balloon artistry,

23
00:02:55.100 --> 00:02:57.190
so it'll take an extraordinary 
feat to please her.

24
00:02:57.430 --> 00:02:59.060
Isn't that right, Your Highness?

25
00:03:00.070 --> 00:03:01.670
Oh, rats!

26
00:03:01.670 --> 00:03:03.620
She's already thinking up her confession!

27
00:03:04.270 --> 00:03:06.150
Okay, here I go.

28
00:03:06.700 --> 00:03:07.620
Hup!

29
00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:19.790
I can't do it...

30
00:03:19.790 --> 00:03:20.510
What?

31
00:03:21.050 --> 00:03:24.090
I'm scared to twist the balloon.

32
00:03:24.090 --> 00:03:26.420
Y-You can do it, Maomao-chan!

33
00:03:26.420 --> 00:03:30.050
There's still room in the balloon 
for the air to escape.

34
00:03:26.470 --> 00:03:27.930
AIR

35
00:03:26.970 --> 00:03:27.930
ROOM

36
00:03:27.970 --> 00:03:32.190
AIR

37
00:03:27.970 --> 00:03:32.190
ROOM

38
00:03:30.050 --> 00:03:32.180
So it won't pop, even if you twist it!

39
00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:34.260
But still...

40
00:03:34.830 --> 00:03:36.650
I'm too scared...

41
00:03:36.650 --> 00:03:38.180
Let me do it!

42
00:03:38.180 --> 00:03:38.860
Your Highness?!

43
00:03:38.860 --> 00:03:41.910
I'll make it and force myself to give in!

44
00:03:41.910 --> 00:03:43.270
You don't see how that's strange?!

45
00:03:43.270 --> 00:03:45.380
What do you want me to do, then?!

46
00:03:45.380 --> 00:03:47.170
Please don't give in!

47
00:03:47.170 --> 00:03:51.550
Maomao-chan's still young, 
so she'll run into things she can't do!

48
00:03:51.550 --> 00:03:56.580
But I don't want her to have bad 
memories of not being able to do it!

49
00:03:57.920 --> 00:04:00.250
Leave everything to me!

50
00:04:00.250 --> 00:04:01.760
You're...

51
00:04:01.760 --> 00:04:03.010
Mama!

52
00:04:04.980 --> 00:04:07.060
Thank you, Princess.

53
00:04:08.010 --> 00:04:10.760
Maomao-chan, let me see that balloon.

54
00:04:13.210 --> 00:04:17.250
You take this, do this, and with that...

55
00:04:19.490 --> 00:04:21.120
Ta-da!

56
00:04:22.030 --> 00:04:24.000
It's a poodle!

57
00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:27.860
Mama sure is amazing...

58
00:04:29.310 --> 00:04:31.000
Maomao-chan.

59
00:04:31.710 --> 00:04:34.330
Next, it's time to bring 
out the big guns.

60
00:04:34.330 --> 00:04:35.540
Huh?

61
00:04:35.540 --> 00:04:38.580
I won't be able to do it all by myself.

62
00:04:39.150 --> 00:04:41.340
Maomao-chan, do you 
think you can help me?

63
00:04:43.470 --> 00:04:44.490
Yeah!

64
00:04:48.610 --> 00:04:50.780
I'll be holding onto this end.

65
00:04:50.780 --> 00:04:53.080
Maomao-chan, try giving it a twist.

66
00:04:53.080 --> 00:04:55.140
Yeah, I'll do my best!

67
00:04:59.900 --> 00:05:01.820
I'm still scared.

68
00:05:01.820 --> 00:05:04.260
Don't worry! I'm right here!

69
00:05:04.260 --> 00:05:06.080
I'm here for you, too.

70
00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:07.940
Y-Yeah...

71
00:05:07.940 --> 00:05:09.700
Twist...

72
00:05:09.960 --> 00:05:11.930
You got this, Maomao-chan!

73
00:05:11.930 --> 00:05:13.710
Twist...

74
00:05:12.860 --> 00:05:14.940
Keep going, Maomao-chan!

75
00:05:14.940 --> 00:05:16.850
Twist...

76
00:05:17.310 --> 00:05:19.540
Twist...

77
00:05:18.410 --> 00:05:19.540
Maomao-chan.

78
00:05:19.540 --> 00:05:20.830
Maomao-chan!

79
00:05:21.150 --> 00:05:23.510
You can do it, Maomao-chan!

80
00:05:26.660 --> 00:05:27.710
I did it!

81
00:05:27.710 --> 00:05:29.140
Good job!

82
00:05:29.140 --> 00:05:31.180
You did it!

83
00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:31.510
Yahoo!

84
00:05:31.510 --> 00:05:35.760
Hooray! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray!

85
00:05:36.070 --> 00:05:39.360
Mama, where do I twist next?

86
00:05:39.810 --> 00:05:41.180
Ta-da!

87
00:05:41.180 --> 00:05:42.760
A flower!

88
00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:44.450
What should we make next?

89
00:05:44.450 --> 00:05:45.630
A teddy bear!

90
00:05:45.630 --> 00:05:49.080
A teddy bear? It won't be easy.

91
00:05:49.080 --> 00:05:53.360
Maomao-chan, do you think 
you can help me a little more?

92
00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:55.270
Yeah, I'll do what I can!

93
00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:56.680
You too, Princess!

94
00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:57.700
Sure!

95
00:06:03.460 --> 00:06:05.920
They all had fun

96
00:06:06.940 --> 00:06:08.140
What?

97
00:06:08.630 --> 00:06:11.430
Forgot to get a secret out of her?

98
00:06:11.430 --> 00:06:12.740
Yes.

99
00:06:12.740 --> 00:06:15.680
Princess Maomao-chan was 
the assigned inquisitor.

100
00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:17.940
She administered balloon art torture...

101
00:06:18.350 --> 00:06:22.800
But after Her Majesty joined in, 
they had so much fun making balloons,

102
00:06:22.800 --> 00:06:26.130
that, apparently, they forgot 
to ask her for a secret.

103
00:06:27.290 --> 00:06:29.270
I see.

104
00:06:30.140 --> 00:06:31.910
Well, it happens to the best—

105
00:06:35.520 --> 00:06:37.420
What's wrong, Your Majesty?!

106
00:06:43.550 --> 00:06:46.000
His Majesty has gotten a mouth ulcer.

107
00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.750
A mouth ulcer?!

108
00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:53.280
His Majesty's mighty jaw and sharp fangs
are said to be able to crush even steel!

109
00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:55.940
An ulcer affecting a mouth like his...

110
00:06:55.940 --> 00:06:58.090
I shudder at the mere thought!

111
00:06:58.090 --> 00:07:03.360
His Majesty can defend himself against 
external attacks with near-instant magic,

112
00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:02.230
<i>Lightning Hurricane</i>

113
00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:05.180
but he's vulnerable from the inside!

114
00:07:05.660 --> 00:07:10.620
And healing magic would 
most likely harm His Majesty.

115
00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:17.020
So the only way is to let His 
Majesty's body heal itself?!

116
00:07:17.020 --> 00:07:20.040
That means he'll need 
to get some quality rest time.

117
00:07:20.040 --> 00:07:22.180
Which in turn means...

118
00:07:24.390 --> 00:07:27.200
He'll need to go on 
special demonic leave!

119
00:07:29.390 --> 00:07:33.600
Demons with sharp fangs are more 
susceptible to mouth and tooth problems,

120
00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:37.340
and demons with many eyes 
are more susceptible to eye conditions.

121
00:07:39.420 --> 00:07:45.630
As such, the Hellhorde offers different 
leave types based on a demon's physiology.

122
00:07:45.630 --> 00:07:49.020
This is known as "special demonic leave."

123
00:07:46.440 --> 00:07:47.520
Special Demonic Leave

124
00:07:49.710 --> 00:07:52.890
The one upside here is 
that today is Friday.

125
00:07:52.890 --> 00:07:55.790
Yes, it won't affect operations too much.

126
00:07:55.790 --> 00:07:57.360
We should manage to hold down 
the fort on our own.

127
00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.450
<i>His Majesty...</i>

128
00:07:59.230 --> 00:08:02.320
<i>I only hope it's nothing serious...</i>

129
00:08:02.610 --> 00:08:04.140
<i>Mr. Hell-Lord?</i>

130
00:08:04.140 --> 00:08:06.490
<i>Mr. Hell-Lord God Thunder?</i>

131
00:08:06.490 --> 00:08:07.920
That's me.

132
00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:11.290
<i>The Hell-Lord's ulcer-afflicted regimen.</i>

133
00:08:11.750 --> 00:08:16.070
<i>Get some relaxing exercise 
to relieve stress.</i>

134
00:08:16.070 --> 00:08:16.870
Oh, hello.

135
00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:17.810
Hello.

136
00:08:18.880 --> 00:08:20.800
Is this okay for you to eat?

137
00:08:21.670 --> 00:08:25.870
<i>Eat soft food that's 
easy on the stomach.</i>

138
00:08:26.390 --> 00:08:28.940
This savory egg custard is delicious.

139
00:08:29.530 --> 00:08:31.060
I'm home!

140
00:08:31.310 --> 00:08:32.580
Welcome back.

141
00:08:32.580 --> 00:08:34.300
Huh? Papa's home!

142
00:08:34.300 --> 00:08:37.410
He came back early 
because he got a mouth ulcer.

143
00:08:37.410 --> 00:08:38.820
Yay!

144
00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:42.750
It really smarts, you know.

145
00:08:42.750 --> 00:08:45.240
Papa! Let's play! Let's play!

146
00:08:45.560 --> 00:08:47.240
Not today.

147
00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:50.340
Once I feel better tomorrow, 
we can play all you like.

148
00:08:50.340 --> 00:08:51.740
Sure thing.

149
00:08:51.740 --> 00:08:54.580
Then I'll help heal your mouth ulcer!

150
00:08:56.570 --> 00:08:59.260
That ulcer doesn't stand a chance.

151
00:09:01.890 --> 00:09:03.820
Brush up top!

152
00:09:02.780 --> 00:09:06.530
<i>Remember to keep good oral hygiene.</i>

153
00:09:04.380 --> 00:09:06.190
Brush down low.

154
00:09:07.370 --> 00:09:09.100
<i>Get plenty of sleep.</i>

155
00:09:10.230 --> 00:09:12.980
Saturday

156
00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:15.490
Papa, are you better now?

157
00:09:15.490 --> 00:09:16.700
Yes.

158
00:09:17.520 --> 00:09:19.300
It's healed up.

159
00:09:19.300 --> 00:09:21.000
Hooray!

160
00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:24.260
Okay, we can play lots today!

161
00:09:24.260 --> 00:09:26.040
Yay!

162
00:09:26.040 --> 00:09:28.080
Woof, woof, woof.

163
00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:30.030
Bow wow wow.

164
00:09:30.030 --> 00:09:31.140
Woof, woof.

165
00:09:31.140 --> 00:09:32.500
Bow wow—

166
00:09:35.760 --> 00:09:37.070
Papa?

167
00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:40.760
It's nothing.

168
00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:43.310
<i>So it still hurts a little?</i>

169
00:09:43.310 --> 00:09:46.160
Maomao-chan, how about you 
and Papa do some drawing?

170
00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:47.060
Sure!

171
00:09:51.910 --> 00:09:53.190
Done!

172
00:09:53.190 --> 00:09:54.950
Let me have a look.

173
00:09:57.580 --> 00:10:00.600
Watch this, Maomao-chan.

174
00:10:03.030 --> 00:10:05.280
What are you folding it for?

175
00:10:06.990 --> 00:10:08.910
Look, a bus.

176
00:10:11.450 --> 00:10:13.250
Beep, beep!

177
00:10:13.610 --> 00:10:15.130
Can I draw people inside?

178
00:10:15.130 --> 00:10:16.480
Yes, go ahead.

179
00:10:17.370 --> 00:10:18.860
Ta-da!

180
00:10:19.870 --> 00:10:21.360
It looks great.

181
00:10:21.880 --> 00:10:24.280
Let me make more cars.

182
00:10:25.910 --> 00:10:27.100
I know!

183
00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:30.540
What's this now, Maomao-chan?

184
00:10:35.850 --> 00:10:37.360
What?!

185
00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:39.520
A tunnel!

186
00:10:40.010 --> 00:10:41.880
<i>Drawing the landscape?</i>

187
00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:46.750
<i>I was too busy focusing on making cars.</i>

188
00:10:46.750 --> 00:10:51.400
<i>By making a tunnel, the scenery 
is suddenly brought into sharp view.</i>

189
00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:56.510
<i>You can practically see the bus 
peacefully driving down a country road.</i>

190
00:10:56.860 --> 00:10:58.830
<i>What creativity!</i>

191
00:10:58.830 --> 00:11:01.270
<i>A feat worthy 
of the Hell-Lord's daughter...</i>

192
00:11:01.270 --> 00:11:04.010
<i>No, of Maomao-chan!</i>

193
00:11:04.450 --> 00:11:07.860
Look, I made Maomao-chan.

194
00:11:07.860 --> 00:11:09.980
Wow! That looks great, Mama!

195
00:11:10.300 --> 00:11:14.330
Let's make lots more 
and turn it into a big town!

196
00:11:14.330 --> 00:11:16.350
Excellent idea.

197
00:11:16.820 --> 00:11:20.520
Create to your heart's content.

198
00:11:20.990 --> 00:11:23.320
Papa, your phone!

199
00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:25.700
Papa, your phone!

200
00:11:24.700 --> 00:11:26.110
Someone's calling?

201
00:11:25.700 --> 00:11:27.340
Papa, your—

202
00:11:27.790 --> 00:11:30.040
Yes, Hell-Lord speaking.

203
00:11:30.270 --> 00:11:31.950
Oh, Your Majesty!

204
00:11:31.790 --> 00:11:40.340
On Duty This Weekend
Chief Battle Officer
Bruse the Destroyer

205
00:11:31.950 --> 00:11:33.720
This is Bruse the Destroyer.

206
00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:35.460
<i>Hard at work, I hope.</i>

207
00:11:35.460 --> 00:11:37.100
<i>Well, what is it?</i>

208
00:11:37.100 --> 00:11:39.460
Oh, well...

209
00:11:39.460 --> 00:11:41.590
I was worried about 
Your Majesty's health

210
00:11:41.590 --> 00:11:43.540
and couldn't help but call.

211
00:11:43.540 --> 00:11:45.910
I see, thanks for calling.

212
00:11:45.910 --> 00:11:47.430
But rest assured.

213
00:11:47.430 --> 00:11:49.350
The pain's already gone.

214
00:11:49.350 --> 00:11:51.300
<i>That's great to hear, Your Majesty!</i>

215
00:11:51.300 --> 00:11:55.340
I'm in the middle 
of constructing a new town.

216
00:11:51.310 --> 00:11:55.350
Chief Battle Officer
Bruse the Destroyer

217
00:11:55.340 --> 00:11:56.500
What?!

218
00:11:56.500 --> 00:11:59.060
Wh-What sort of town?

219
00:11:59.640 --> 00:12:04.110
A town filled to the brim 
with every desire imaginable.

220
00:12:04.630 --> 00:12:06.450
Unbelievable!

221
00:12:06.750 --> 00:12:09.220
<i>I'll see you on Monday.</i>

222
00:12:13.410 --> 00:12:17.030
What does he mean by a town?

223
00:12:18.100 --> 00:12:21.350
Let's get back to building our town.

224
00:12:21.350 --> 00:12:22.940
Yay!

225
00:12:34.810 --> 00:12:37.400
Sunday

226
00:12:37.690 --> 00:12:40.410
One, two, three, four.

227
00:12:44.370 --> 00:12:45.820
There we go!

228
00:12:47.380 --> 00:12:49.740
Well done.

229
00:12:55.610 --> 00:12:58.330
All that playtime with 
you made her really happy.

230
00:13:00.330 --> 00:13:01.950
That makes two of us.

231
00:13:05.500 --> 00:13:10.110
When I first got the mouth ulcer, 
I was prepared for the worst.

232
00:13:10.110 --> 00:13:14.910
But as a result, I got to spend 
lots of time with Maomao-chan.

233
00:13:14.910 --> 00:13:16.280
Isn't that nice?

234
00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:21.570
It <i>is</i> a little tough not being able to 
watch late-night anime live, though.

235
00:13:21.900 --> 00:13:25.380
You should stop staying up so late 
and get to bed earlier from now on.

236
00:13:25.380 --> 00:13:27.430
That I can't promise.

237
00:13:27.430 --> 00:13:28.160
What?

238
00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:32.320
Instead, I'll cut down 
on midnight snacks.

239
00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:33.900
That's for the best.

240
00:13:35.950 --> 00:13:39.630
Lulune, you should watch out 
for mouth ulcers, too.

241
00:13:39.630 --> 00:13:40.820
Will do.

242
00:13:41.170 --> 00:13:43.420
Monday

243
00:13:41.170 --> 00:13:43.420
Bus Stop

244
00:13:41.170 --> 00:13:43.420
Hell-Lord Residence

245
00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:47.110
Papa, will you be home early today?

246
00:13:47.110 --> 00:13:51.810
My mouth ulcer's healed up, 
so I'm working normal hours today.

247
00:13:52.180 --> 00:13:53.850
I see...

248
00:13:53.850 --> 00:13:55.560
Oh, I know!

249
00:13:55.560 --> 00:13:58.950
You should get lots 
of mouth ulcers from now on!

250
00:14:00.440 --> 00:14:04.110
A devilish request 
behind an angelic smile.

251
00:14:09.530 --> 00:14:12.090
What? His Majesty?!

252
00:14:12.090 --> 00:14:12.520
Yes!

253
00:14:12.520 --> 00:14:15.430
He's returned from the depths of hell!

254
00:14:18.040 --> 00:14:20.880
Certificate of Health

255
00:14:18.040 --> 00:14:20.880
Attn: Hellhorde

256
00:14:18.040 --> 00:14:20.880
Patient Name: Hell-Lord God Thunder

257
00:14:18.040 --> 00:14:20.880
Patient was diagnosed with condition: (     stomatitis     ).
Following treatment, patient has recuperated and fully recovered from the condition stated above.

258
00:14:18.450 --> 00:14:20.880
The certificate 
for your healed mouth ulcer.

259
00:14:20.880 --> 00:14:23.120
Everything looks to be in order.

260
00:14:24.090 --> 00:14:28.560
Please accept my deepest congratulations 
on your recovery, Your Majesty!

261
00:14:31.170 --> 00:14:34.060
I'm back to 100 percent!

262
00:14:37.980 --> 00:14:40.020
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

263
00:14:40.730 --> 00:14:43.770
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

264
00:14:43.770 --> 00:14:45.530
Okay, do your worst!

265
00:14:45.530 --> 00:14:47.210
Oh, that's right.

266
00:14:47.210 --> 00:14:51.470
Last weekend, we went through 
the ordeal of His Majesty falling ill.

267
00:14:51.470 --> 00:14:53.320
Hey, is he all right?

268
00:14:53.320 --> 00:14:55.450
Your Highness, we're talking 
about the Hell-Lord here!

269
00:14:55.450 --> 00:14:57.200
He's the last person 
you should worry about!

270
00:14:57.540 --> 00:15:00.490
Fortunately, he was able to 
make a full recovery.

271
00:15:00.870 --> 00:15:02.310
Good to hear.

272
00:15:02.310 --> 00:15:03.960
No, not good!

273
00:15:04.190 --> 00:15:07.590
As for me, I work out on a regular basis.

274
00:15:07.590 --> 00:15:10.420
I've never once gotten sick—

275
00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:15.080
Your Highness?!

276
00:15:15.080 --> 00:15:16.440
What's the matter?

277
00:15:16.800 --> 00:15:18.040
This is...

278
00:15:18.790 --> 00:15:20.430
Jinx-eye!

279
00:15:20.560 --> 00:15:22.900
Jinx-Eye

280
00:15:22.890 --> 00:15:24.780
Jinx-eye?!

281
00:15:24.780 --> 00:15:25.900
What in the world is that?

282
00:15:25.900 --> 00:15:27.890
It hurts...

283
00:15:27.890 --> 00:15:31.700
'Tis a disease where part of the eyelid 
turns red and swollen from inflammation.

284
00:15:32.890 --> 00:15:34.690
You mean a stye?

285
00:15:34.690 --> 00:15:36.280
So that's what you call it 
in the Demon World.

286
00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:38.740
My eye hurts...

287
00:15:38.740 --> 00:15:40.040
Please rest assured.

288
00:15:40.740 --> 00:15:43.710
It'll heal in no time 
with some eye drops.

289
00:15:52.500 --> 00:15:53.630
Princess.

290
00:15:54.160 --> 00:15:56.210
Could it be that you 
can't handle eye drops?

291
00:15:57.470 --> 00:15:59.380
Are you scared to take them?

292
00:16:01.770 --> 00:16:05.600
Her Highness is Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

293
00:16:05.600 --> 00:16:08.410
The very image of bravery! 
Fearless and dashing!

294
00:16:08.410 --> 00:16:11.780
Her Highness would never cower 
at the sight of eye drops!

295
00:16:11.780 --> 00:16:12.720
Right, Your Highness?

296
00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:14.160
I'm scared of eye drops.

297
00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:15.080
Your Highness?

298
00:16:15.080 --> 00:16:18.790
I'm terrified of the idea 
of sticking something in my eye...

299
00:16:18.790 --> 00:16:19.750
How can that be?!

300
00:16:20.390 --> 00:16:23.020
Through sandstorms and downpours alike,

301
00:16:23.020 --> 00:16:26.500
you would stare down your enemy 
without ever averting your gaze!

302
00:16:26.500 --> 00:16:29.010
But eye drops you put in yourself!

303
00:16:29.260 --> 00:16:33.480
And all while staring down 
the droplet about to enter your eye...

304
00:16:33.480 --> 00:16:34.420
It's scary!

305
00:16:34.420 --> 00:16:37.890
The sheer fear always makes me 
lose all strength in my hand!

306
00:16:37.890 --> 00:16:43.450
It's exactly the same as putting a gun 
to your head and pulling the trigger!

307
00:16:43.450 --> 00:16:44.850
It's nothing like that, actually!

308
00:16:46.550 --> 00:16:50.340
I see, so you're scared of 
putting in eye drops yourself.

309
00:16:54.830 --> 00:16:56.490
Torture...

310
00:16:56.490 --> 00:16:57.570
Don't worry.

311
00:16:57.960 --> 00:17:01.830
As long as you keep your eyes open, 
you don't need to look right at it.

312
00:17:02.250 --> 00:17:05.410
Just look right at the bunny.

313
00:17:05.810 --> 00:17:07.040
Sure...

314
00:17:22.710 --> 00:17:24.150
You're done?

315
00:17:24.150 --> 00:17:26.700
Yes, you did great.

316
00:17:26.700 --> 00:17:29.510
Please keep your eyes shut.

317
00:17:31.560 --> 00:17:35.250
<i>A pleasant feeling 
spreading across my eye.</i>

318
00:17:35.800 --> 00:17:41.450
<i>With my eyes closed, a refreshing 
sensation floods this world of darkness.</i>

319
00:17:42.220 --> 00:17:44.860
<i>Feels so good...</i>

320
00:17:47.180 --> 00:17:48.870
Thanks, Torture.

321
00:17:48.870 --> 00:17:50.210
Think nothing of it.

322
00:17:50.210 --> 00:17:52.700
I know how painful jinx-eye can be.

323
00:17:52.990 --> 00:17:54.870
Oh yeah, a secret...

324
00:17:55.900 --> 00:17:59.060
I ask you to divulge a secret 
only during our torture sessions.

325
00:17:59.570 --> 00:18:01.090
Torture...

326
00:18:01.680 --> 00:18:04.710
You really are such a softie.

327
00:18:04.710 --> 00:18:07.820
There's no guarantee 
that I'll fold today, you know?

328
00:18:07.820 --> 00:18:11.010
I'll make you regret not asking
me for a secret here.

329
00:18:11.690 --> 00:18:13.700
I look forward to it.

330
00:18:13.700 --> 00:18:17.950
No matter the torture, 
I will never give in!

331
00:18:19.070 --> 00:18:22.030
The princess
confessed

332
00:18:22.370 --> 00:18:26.230
A quirk in the Imperial 
Army's marching pattern?

333
00:18:26.990 --> 00:18:29.430
More useless information.

334
00:18:31.380 --> 00:18:36.090
I'm more surprised to hear 
the princess can't handle eye drops.

335
00:18:36.090 --> 00:18:37.040
Indeed.

336
00:18:37.320 --> 00:18:41.050
I hear she was only able to 
take them with Torture's aid.

337
00:18:41.050 --> 00:18:42.700
Oh?

338
00:18:43.320 --> 00:18:45.220
She managed to take them?

339
00:18:45.220 --> 00:18:46.980
How admirable.

340
00:20:22.900 --> 00:20:28.280
My fever's gone down, 
but my throat still feels uncomfortable.

341
00:20:28.670 --> 00:20:32.960
It may be my day off, 
but I'll have to take it easy today.

342
00:20:35.930 --> 00:20:40.520
My appetite's returned, so I should 
feel better soon with a bit of rest.

343
00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:47.370
I had saved some frozen udon.

344
00:20:52.050 --> 00:20:55.390
Simmer slowly until the broth melts.

345
00:20:56.090 --> 00:20:59.530
Once it does, turn it up 
to medium heat to finish cooking.

346
00:21:01.420 --> 00:21:04.040
It's starting to smell great.

347
00:21:04.680 --> 00:21:06.320
Once everything's up to a boil...

348
00:21:06.900 --> 00:21:08.360
It's ready to eat!

349
00:21:13.210 --> 00:21:15.040
Hot! Hot, hot!

350
00:21:17.800 --> 00:21:20.130
That was hotter than I expected.

351
00:21:20.490 --> 00:21:23.370
I should have just used oven mitts.

352
00:21:23.630 --> 00:21:26.090
Shichimi 
Pepper

353
00:21:26.630 --> 00:21:29.320
Okay, let's dig in.

354
00:21:30.350 --> 00:21:32.220
Shichimi 
Pepper

355
00:21:32.680 --> 00:21:35.380
I brought out 
the shichimi by force of habit.

356
00:21:35.380 --> 00:21:37.390
I'll have to pass for today.

357
00:21:51.740 --> 00:21:53.190
It's delicious!

358
00:22:01.730 --> 00:22:04.110
It's soaking right into my aching body.

359
00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:06.500
Next up is...

360
00:22:07.020 --> 00:22:08.930
Oh, the shrimp tempura...

361
00:22:11.050 --> 00:22:17.440
I hate to waste food, but my stomach's 
still weak, so I shouldn't eat it.

362
00:22:19.810 --> 00:22:20.800
Still...

363
00:22:21.560 --> 00:22:23.340
It looks so good...

364
00:22:24.620 --> 00:22:25.880
I mustn't!

365
00:22:25.880 --> 00:22:28.740
I am the Hellhorde's grand inquisitor!

366
00:22:28.740 --> 00:22:30.920
My self-control is ironclad!

367
00:22:31.280 --> 00:22:34.900
I won't give in to desire 
and behave foolishly!

368
00:22:45.070 --> 00:22:47.230
Oh, I'm powerless!

369
00:22:47.230 --> 00:22:48.520
It's too good!

370
00:22:49.350 --> 00:22:52.660
The soft batter that's 
soaked up all the broth.

371
00:22:52.660 --> 00:22:57.920
The undersized shrimp that still asserts 
its presence with its plump texture.

372
00:22:58.400 --> 00:23:00.140
It's perfect.

373
00:23:01.110 --> 00:23:05.430
I'll drink plenty of water 
and pray that I don't upset my stomach.

374
00:23:09.250 --> 00:23:11.060
That was great.

375
00:23:11.740 --> 00:23:13.620
My stomach feels so warm.

376
00:23:14.970 --> 00:23:16.550
Thank you for the wonderful meal.

377
00:23:16.960 --> 00:23:21.150
Now to spend the day resting up in bed.

378
00:23:23.420 --> 00:23:26.210
It's a shame that I can't go outside,

379
00:23:26.780 --> 00:23:30.870
but sleeping all I want while the 
sun's still up is a thrill in itself.

380
00:23:38.710 --> 00:23:43.710
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

381
00:23:39.270 --> 00:23:43.710
<i>Torture got plenty of sleep 
and got better.</i>

